words also about our specialist

00:05:54.150 --> 00:05:57.180
in all our three sections,
the African,

00:05:57.180 --> 00:05:59.860
the Near East, and
the Hebraic section.

00:05:59.860 --> 00:06:01.910
They're all scholars themselves.

00:06:01.910 --> 00:06:03.210
They have written.

00:06:03.210 --> 00:06:04.510
They have published.

00:06:04.510 --> 00:06:05.810
They are quoted in books.

00:06:05.810 --> 00:06:07.900
And they know the society
and the culture

00:06:07.900 --> 00:06:10.360
and the languages of the region.

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:16.680
So our scholar, Dr. Muhannad
Salhi, will introduce the speaker

00:06:16.680 --> 00:06:20.760
and the film producer
today, Muhannad.

