00:07:37.430 --> 00:07:41.190
Just a few words about
the documentary film

00:07:41.190 --> 00:07:42.730
that we're going to be seeing.

00:07:42.730 --> 00:07:48.850
It's short, 16 minutes and its
entitled "Madame Parliamentarian".

00:07:48.850 --> 00:07:54.660
Just to give you a general context,
I usually like to take Q and A's

00:07:54.660 --> 00:08:00.590
after the film but just to
give you a general setting,

00:08:00.590 --> 00:08:06.260
it was filmed during two
- the last two elections

00:08:06.260 --> 00:08:10.630
of Lebanon, 2005 and 2009.

00:08:10.630 --> 00:08:18.810 position:56%
And it focuses on the participation
of women in the Lebanese parliament.

00:08:18.810 --> 00:08:25.020
I'll just say a couple of things
about the general political

00:08:25.020 --> 00:08:30.730
or parliamentarian
system in Lebanon.

00:08:31.750 --> 00:08:35.540
In general, Lebanon is
-- population consist

00:08:35.540 --> 00:08:41.070
of we just say roughly
50% Christian, 50% Muslim

00:08:41.070 --> 00:08:42.790
and the distribution of the seats

00:08:42.790 --> 00:08:46.030
in the Lebanese parliament
try to reflect that.

00:08:46.030 --> 00:08:54.510
So the way the seats are identified
or located follow a religious quota

00:08:54.510 --> 00:08:57.360
in a way so though the
terms confessionalism

00:08:57.360 --> 00:09:03.370
or sectarianism will be mentioned
a couple of times in the film

00:09:03.370 --> 00:09:06.440
and probably by me
in the Q and A after

00:09:06.440 --> 00:09:09.260
and that's what these
terms refer to.

00:09:09.260 --> 00:09:12.760
I know that for some people in
the United States or other places,

00:09:12.760 --> 00:09:17.000 position:56%
they might not be familiar with the
term confessionalism or sectarianism

00:09:17.000 --> 00:09:18.470
and that's what it refers to.

00:09:18.470 --> 00:09:21.810
It's basically how the parliament,

00:09:21.810 --> 00:09:24.500
the seats in the parliament
have certain quotas

00:09:24.500 --> 00:09:30.250
to reflect the religious diversity
of the population in Lebanon.

00:09:30.250 --> 00:09:34.660
I think I'll leave it at that
for now and watch the film

00:09:34.660 --> 00:09:36.180
and we can discuss later.

00:09:36.180 --> 00:09:37.980
Thank you.

