00:25:25.110 --> 00:25:29.800
And under Christians, there are
majority Maronite Catholics,

00:25:29.800 --> 00:25:34.200
East Orthodox, Greek
Orthodox, Catholic Orthodox,

00:25:34.200 --> 00:25:37.330
there are various churches
