00:50:08.030 --> 00:50:11.960
who could be born and
could be living in Lebanon.

00:50:11.960 --> 00:50:15.030
So that passing of
citizenship from a woman

00:50:15.030 --> 00:50:18.570
to her family is right now absent.

00:50:18.570 --> 00:50:20.010
It's always been absent.

00:50:20.010 --> 00:50:24.750
While a man can very simply marry
a foreign woman give her Lebanese

00:50:24.750 --> 00:50:27.720
citizenship and the children,
of course, will be born

00:50:27.720 --> 00:50:31.620
and because he is a male father,
he could pass on his citizenship.

00:50:31.620 --> 00:50:35.920
So these are like the main
two big issues that in terms

00:50:35.920 --> 00:50:40.400
of women's rights are being
by parliament to be adjusted.

